title: They Don’t See What I See
itunes:title: They Don’t See What I See
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m dating a wealthy, handsome and very powerful man. He’s a popular motivational speaker and life coach online and in our small community. We’ve been together for close to 5 years and he gave me an engagement ring last month to stall me out. As his popularity grew, his personality grew. I don’t know the man that I live with now and his followers don’t see what I see.............................
